## More information ##
Dux is fully [Open-source software](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_software), released under the [MIT/X11 license](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MIT_License).
The source is available at [http://github.com/RockerMONO/dux](http://github.com/RockerMONO/dux).

